BLACK DIAMOND OIL TRUST NO. 513, G. S. Willhoite, Trustee, Petitioner, v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE, Respondent. No. 7021. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Dec. 5, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Cüv cult Judges, and CAYANAH, District Judge,

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for respondent, consented to by counsel for petitioner, ordered petition to review herein dismissed for failure of petitioner to file record and docket cause.
